    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Fair-condition driver that is usable and presentable, but it shows its age throughout. Expect visible cosmetic flaws in the paint and body, wear inside, and the kind of older-driver imperfections you\u2019d expect from a car that has been used rather than preserved. This is not a show car, but it should appeal to someone looking for an affordable entry point and a car they can enjoy while improving over time. Best for a buyer who wants a solid driver and is comfortable addressing cosmetic and maintenance needs as they come up.",
