    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Absolutely gorgeous and exceptionally well-kept, this mint-condition car is a fantastic find for anyone wanting something that feels close to new. It presents beautifully, has clearly been very well cared for, and stands out for its overall cleanliness and condition. A sharp, high-quality car that should make its next owner very happy.",
