      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Well-suited for a value-focused buyer, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point with solid potential for everyday use, a work commute, or a hands-on project. It presents as an honest, budget-friendly option for someone who appreciates straightforward value and the chance to make it their own. Priced to reflect its condition while still delivering real usefulness, this is a practical opportunity to secure transportation at a highly accessible price.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, moves, and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants inexpensive wheels, a handy project, or a practical backup vehicle. It\u2019s being advertised honestly and priced accordingly, so there are no surprises here\u2014just a straightforward car from a straightforward seller. If you want something affordable and usable without spending a fortune, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with great bones and plenty of upside for the right buyer. Starts, moves, and offers a straightforward platform for a budget build, parts runner, or weekend wrenching project. Engine bay is complete, drivetrain feels like a workable foundation, and the chassis has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s been used rather than hidden. Not a showroom piece, but a compelling entry point for someone who values mechanical simplicity and the chance to improve it over time. Priced to sell for an enthusiast who sees the potential.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast. Sold as-is.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car with stories in its steel and plenty of life left for the right driver. Honest, seasoned, and full of character, it has the sort of road-worn presence that turns a simple commute into something with a little more soul. Perfect as a budget-friendly daily, first car, or weekend project, it offers a chance to get behind the wheel without stretching your wallet. If you appreciate a vehicle with grit, personality, and room to make it your own, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical low-cost option for buyers seeking basic transportation or a project with potential. It shows clear signs of age and use, but presents a strong value proposition for someone who prioritizes budget over cosmetics. A sensible choice for an economical runabout, work vehicle, or starter project at a very accessible price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    }
